The package boost-poly-collection is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS poly_collection)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::poly_collection)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_poly_collection REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::poly_collection)
